thread 'main' panicked at src\main.rs:37:51:
called `Result::unwrap()` on an `Err` value: Error("type `bevy_reflect_test::Vector2Wrapper` is not registered in the type registry (stack: `bevy_reflect_test::Port2` -> `bevy_reflect_test::Vector2Wrapper`)", line: 0, column: 0)
stack backtrace:
